{"tid":645193,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【宣示主權？】放閃着情侶裝畀人睇　專家：好似狗戴頸圈一樣","createTime":"2018-04-28T02:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T03:14:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a88354c09250ef0c941de38bcb1711114ae8fda8","tid":645193,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T02:12:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20180428/20375024?_ga=2.190782187.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F20375024%3F_ga%3D2.190782187.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435&d=3Zcl6KWI0%2FyePqdkTz%2Bzb2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5b9025c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F20375024%3F_ga%3D2.190782187.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435&h=b2e3b435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20180428/20375024?_ga=2.190782187.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【宣示主權？】放閃着情侶裝畀人睇　專家：好似狗戴頸圈一樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180428/large/sub72501.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180428%2Flarge%2Fsub72501.jpg&h=1009d849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n情侶裝冇分對錯，情侶嘛，向來都是放閃有理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情侶裝如同一個品味，各有捧場客，無分對錯，情侶嘛，向來都是放閃有理，真的要談論的話，應該是美感多於是非黑白。行為反映心態，背後當然都有得解，臨床身心行為學家李寶能指，這是一個彼此想成為命運共同體的慾望，不容他人介入，即是向外人宣示：「我哋一齊的，你唔好騷擾我哋。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180428/large/sub72502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180428%2Flarge%2Fsub72502.jpg&h=9e86dfaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n臨床身心行為學家李寶能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他又指，情侶裝如同符號，俗點講句，真係去到邊都認到，「好似狗有頸圈一樣，差在沒有狗繩，或頸圈上有主人的號碼。」比喻而已。另外，行為背後也牽涉情侶間的主次或從屬關係，即是上下把位。雙方都想當然皆大歡喜，若然其中一方不情不願，只是出於妥協，那情侶裝的原意就不成立了，所反映的只是二人於感情上的地位之差。<br />\n<br />\n最後他強調，作為一種玩意的話，情侶裝可以是感情的調味劑，宜輕鬆對待，「但如果你好認真，只是為了一件小事而吵大架，甚至分道揚鏢，冇朋友做，仲講咩情侶呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者：湯珮然<br />\n攝影：劉永發、徐振國、鄭明川<br />\n<br />\n全新旅遊專頁，即like籽想旅行：<a href=\"https://fb.com/travel.appleseed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Ftravel.appleseed&d=3Zcl6KWI0%2FyePqdkTz%2Bzb2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8fd87728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/travel.appleseed</a>"},{"pid":"4fd0e2749370302d2e113f9b1e5d9997537013e9","tid":645193,"uid":97537,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T02:19:18.000Z","msg":"個專家做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0fc9a6c64a1d71d560ced9bf044a505f88d895","tid":645193,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"結論：連登仔無女-＞養狗-＞O1"},{"pid":"8d2a9bb3c7a509b8176661c33a0fe1c5288044e9","tid":645193,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T03:14:59.000Z","msg":"以為換左個專家幅圖<br />\n<br />\n點知原來係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}